        <p id="Par27">First, we considered a case without observation noise, with only Poisson noise from the infection process itself (see “<xref rid="Sec36" ref-type="sec">Appendix C</xref>” section for details). This constitutes an ideal case where we expect <inline-formula id="IEq26"><alternatives><tex-math id="M49">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
