        <p id="Par29">Note that, when using estimateR, it is not recommended to smooth observations that do not exhibit strong observation noise, as this decreases the ability to detect rapid changes in <inline-formula id="IEq35"><alternatives><tex-math id="M73">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
