      <sec id="Sec16">
        <title>Handling truncated incidence data</title>
        <p id="Par38">To investigate the impact of extrapolating observation counts that were truncated off, we assumed a constant <inline-formula id="IEq59"><alternatives><tex-math id="M139">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
