      </sec>
      <sec id="Sec18">
        <title>Dealing with partially-delayed observations</title>
        <p id="Par40">Finally, we investigated the impact of nowcasting unseen partially-delayed observations before smoothing instead of after. To do so, we performed simulations of partially-delayed and fully-delayed observations with <inline-formula id="IEq65"><alternatives><tex-math id="M155">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
