    <sec id="Sec19">
      <title>Comparison with other methods</title>
      <sec id="Sec20">
        <title>Comparison on simulated data</title>
        <p id="Par41">We compared the accuracy of estimates from estimateR against epidemia [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="CR15">15</xref>] and EpiNow2 [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="CR16">16</xref>], two prominent and recently-developed R packages for <inline-formula id="IEq67"><alternatives><tex-math id="M159">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
