        <p id="Par51">For comparison, we also obtained estimates from the publicly available EpiForecasts dashboard by Abbott et al. [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="CR20">20</xref>], which uses EpiNow2 as an underlying <inline-formula id="IEq75"><alternatives><tex-math id="M197">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
				\usepackage{amssymb} 
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
