            <p id="Par73">estimateR implements a wrapper around the method developed by Cori et al. [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="CR8">8</xref>], implemented in the EpiEstim R package, to estimate <inline-formula id="IEq167"><alternatives><tex-math id="M325">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
