            <p id="Par74">Disease transmission is modelled with a Poisson process. An individual infected at time <inline-formula id="IEq168"><alternatives><tex-math id="M327">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
