				\begin{document}$$O_{t}$$\end{document}</tex-math><mml:math id="M464"><mml:msub><mml:mi>O</mml:mi><mml:mi>t</mml:mi></mml:msub></mml:math><inline-graphic xlink:href="12859_2023_5428_Article_IEq232.gif"/></alternatives></inline-formula> is computed from the generated observations <inline-formula id="IEq233"><alternatives><tex-math id="M465">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
