          </sec>
        </sec>
        <sec id="Sec40">
          <title>Appendix D: default settings</title>
          <p id="Par95">In estimateR, by default, the most recent <inline-formula id="IEq235"><alternatives><tex-math id="M471">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
