        <p id="Par31">We simulated pairs of partially-delayed and fully-delayed time series as described in “<xref rid="Sec36" ref-type="sec">Appendix C</xref>” section. We tested four scenarios with varying fractions of partially-delayed observations <italic>p</italic>: 0, 0.3, 0.6, 1. The parameter setting <inline-formula id="IEq40"><alternatives><tex-math id="M83">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
