      <sec id="Sec14">
        <title>Validation on simulated data generated with time-varying delay distributions</title>
        <p id="Par33">Finally, we investigated the effect of time-varying delay distributions on the estimation of <inline-formula id="IEq51"><alternatives><tex-math id="M113">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
