        <p id="Par42">As before, we simulated outbreaks following five different <inline-formula id="IEq68"><alternatives><tex-math id="M161">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
