				\begin{document}$$R_{e}$$\end{document}</tex-math><mml:math id="M350"><mml:msub><mml:mi>R</mml:mi><mml:mi>e</mml:mi></mml:msub></mml:math><inline-graphic xlink:href="12859_2023_5428_Article_IEq177.gif"/></alternatives></inline-formula> estimate for time step <italic>T</italic> summarises the average estimated <inline-formula id="IEq178"><alternatives><tex-math id="M351">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
