				\begin{document}$$\tau$$\end{document}</tex-math><mml:math id="M354"><mml:mi>τ</mml:mi></mml:math><inline-graphic xlink:href="12859_2023_5428_Article_IEq179.gif"/></alternatives></inline-formula> time steps ending on time step <italic>T</italic>. By default in estimateR, <inline-formula id="IEq180"><alternatives><tex-math id="M355">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
